VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)-keepclassmembers\s+class\s+[^\n{]*(?:password|secret|token|apikey)[^\n{]*
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects missing obfuscation for sensitive classes or methods.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Missing Obfuscation for Sensitive Classes.
